posting_body: ['To schedule a tour', 'We now book our tour appointments online!', 'Please call or text us at', 'show contact info', 'to self-schedule from your phone!', 'Book your appointment online today or anytime 24/7!', 'Property Description', 'Radius At The Domain offers spacious 1, 2, and 3 bedroom floor plans featuring modern cabinetry, designer lighting, wood vinyl planking, and full-sized washer and dryer*.', 'Just a short walk away from the Domain shopping district, the Arboretum and major thoroughfares (US183, Loop 1/Mopac, and IH-35) Radius At The Domain is located in the award-winning Austin Independent School District.', 'Our elegant, pet-friendly apartments deliver a full list of amenities.', 'Choose Radius At The Domain, Live Happy!', 'Details', 'Availability date:', 'August 22, 2022', 'Pets:', 'Cats, Small Dogs (< 25lb), Large Dogs (> 25lb)', 'Pet notes:', 'Pets - Max 2 allowed, One time Fee $400.00, Rent $25.00Comments: We love your well behaved pets!', 'Roscoe Property Management welcomes all dog breeds, ages, and sizes.', 'Pet interview required.', 'All fees are per pet.', 'Deposit:', '$400 Traditional OR $100 eDeposit through ePremium Insurance', 'Leasing options:', 'Leasing notes:', 'Application fee:', '$50 per person 18 yrs.', 'of age or older', 'Amenities', 'Included in Utilities Cost:', 'Utilities Cost:', 'Laundry:', 'In Unit, Shared', 'Parking type:', 'Covered, Off-Street', 'Parking notes:', 'Free Uncovered-$30 Covered', 'Appliances:', 'Dishwasher, Refrigerator, Garbage disposal, Microwave, Range/Oven', 'Exterior:', 'Balcony/patio', 'Heating/cooling:', 'Heat: forced air, Central AC, Air conditioning', 'Wiring:', 'Facilities and Recreation:', 'Shared pool, Fitness center, Clubhouse, Playground, Barbecue, Business center', 'Security and Access:', 'Gated entry', 'Views:', 'Additional features:', 'Hardwood floor, Granite countertop', 'Offered by:', 'Radius at the Domain', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
